<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Magic Link - Gardeners for Africa Portal</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2d5a3d;
            background-color: #f7f8f3;
        }
        
        /* Container */
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(45, 90, 61, 0.16);
        }
        
        /* Header with gradient background */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d5a3d 0%, #3a6b4a 50%, #5d4e37 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #f7f8f3;
        }
        
        .logo {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background-color: rgba(247, 248, 243, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .logo-text {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #f7f8f3;
        }
        
        .welcome-title {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #f7f8f3;
        }
        
        .welcome-subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: rgba(247, 248, 243, 0.9);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        /* Main content */
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d5a3d;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a5d4a;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        /* Magic link info */
        .magic-info {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #0ea5e9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .magic-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .magic-title {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .magic-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        /* CTA Button */
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d5a3d, #3a6b4a);
            color: #f7f8f3;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45, 90, 61, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45, 90, 61, 0.4);
        }
        
        /* Alternative link */
        .alternative-link {
            background-color: #f7f8f3;
            border: 1px solid #e8ebe8;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        
        .alternative-link-title {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d5a3d;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .alternative-link-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7c6b;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        
        /* Expiry notice */
        .expiry-notice {
            background-color: #f7f8f3;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 4px solid #2d5a3d;
        }
        
        .expiry-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7c6b;
        }
        
        .expiry-time {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d5a3d;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        
        /* Security notice */
        .security-notice {
            background-color: #fef3e2;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .security-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .security-title {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .security-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #92400e;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background-color: #f7f8f3;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e8ebe8;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7c6b;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #2d5a3d;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .footer-address {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #8a9a8a;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        
        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .welcome-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .logo-text {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">‚ú®</div>
                <div class="logo-text">Gardeners for Africa Portal</div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="welcome-title">Your Magic Link is Ready!</h1>
            <p class="welcome-subtitle">Click the button below to securely access your account without a password.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="greeting">Hello {{firstName}}!</h2>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>You requested a magic link to access your <strong>Gardeners for Africa Portal</strong> account. This secure link will log you in automatically without requiring a password.</p>
                
                <p>Simply click the button below to access your account. This link is unique to you and will work only once for security purposes.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Magic Link Info -->
            <div class="magic-info">
                <span class="magic-icon">üîó</span>
                <h3 class="magic-title">What is a Magic Link?</h3>
                <p class="magic-text">
                    A magic link is a secure, passwordless way to access your account. It's safer than traditional passwords and more convenient. 
                    This link is unique to you and expires automatically for security.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{magicUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access My Account</a>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Alternative Link -->
            <div class="alternative-link">
                <div class="alternative-link-title">Can't click the button?</div>
                <div class="alternative-link-text">Copy and paste this link into your browser: {{magicUrl}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Expiry Notice -->
            <div class="expiry-notice">
                <p class="expiry-text">This magic link expires in:</p>
                <div class="expiry-time">{{expiryTime}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Security Notice -->
            <div class="security-notice">
                <span class="security-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
                <h3 class="security-title">Security Information</h3>
                <p class="security-text">
                    This magic link is unique to you and will only work once. If you didn't request this link, 
                    please contact our support team immediately. Never share this link with anyone.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p><strong>Note:</strong> If you didn't request this magic link, you can safely ignore this email. Your account remains secure.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                This is an automated message from Gardeners for Africa Portal. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
            
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="{{supportUrl}}" class="footer-link">Support Center</a>
                <a href="{{helpUrl}}" class="footer-link">Help Documentation</a>
                <a href="{{contactUrl}}" class="footer-link">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-address">
                <p>Gardeners for Africa Education Platform</p>
                <p>Transforming Education Across Africa</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
